013  public StringProjection<CategoryProjectionRoot<PARENT, ROOT>, CategoryProjectionRoot<PARENT, ROOT>> name(
014      String locale, List<String> acceptLanguage) {
015    StringProjection<CategoryProjectionRoot<PARENT, ROOT>, CategoryProjectionRoot<PARENT, ROOT>> projection = new StringProjection<>(this, this);    
016    getFields().put("name", projection);
017    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("name", k -> new ArrayList<>());                      
018    InputArgument localeArg = new InputArgument("locale", locale);
019    getInputArguments().get("name").add(localeArg);
020    InputArgument acceptLanguageArg = new InputArgument("acceptLanguage", acceptLanguage);
021    getInputArguments().get("name").add(acceptLanguageArg);
022    return projection;
023  }
